channel.title: Gay error in the CMD, No clue what causes it
channel.description:
Hey umm, can someone care to help me? I get this error when I try to run some bat file called Export new cache, has to do with model making. And also when I try to run servers. Can you help me out?
Exporting New Cache Files.
[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: cacheexport2/Main Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: cacheexport2.Main at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClassInternal(Unknown Source) Could not find the main class: cacheexport2.Main. Program will exit.
Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
